---
// How Lessons Work component
---

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">How Lessons Work</h2>
    <div class="content-text">
      <p>Each lesson combines different learning elements to help students understand the topic.</p>
      <p>Lessons include:</p>
      
      <div class="lesson-features">
        <div class="feature-item">• instructional videos</div>
        <div class="feature-item">• explanations and learning material</div>
        <div class="feature-item">• quizzes and multiple choice questions</div>
        <div class="feature-item">• interactive tasks inside the learning world</div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="process-explanation">Students follow the lesson while exploring the island environment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .content-section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95), rgba(255,255,255,0.85));
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: #2c3e50;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .content-text {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #34495e;
  }

  .content-text p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .lesson-features {
    margin: 30px 0;
    padding: 30px;
    background: rgba(52,73,94,0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(52,73,94,0.1);
  }

  .feature-item {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2980b9;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .feature-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .feature-item::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #3498db;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .process-explanation {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #7f8c8d;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content-text {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .lesson-features {
      padding: 20px 15px;
    }

    .feature-item {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding-left: 15px;
    }

    .feature-item::before {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>